        <field>Action_Description__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Ensure all transmission of cardholder data across open public networks uses strong cryptography including TLS 1.2 or higher. PCI DSS requires that sensitive authentication data is never transmitted in cleartext.</value>
