    <values>
        <field>Remediation_Steps__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Verify that all Salesforce API integrations handling cardholder data use TLS 1.2 or higher by reviewing Named Credential and External Service configurations. Enable Shield Platform Encryption for fields storing any payment-related data at rest. Audit all outbound callouts to payment processors to confirm they use HTTPS endpoints exclusively. Disable any legacy TLS versions in your org session security settings.</value>
